results.title: Add-On - Various Band Charms for Midori or Fauxdori Traveller's Notebooks
results.description:
Please note these are only available as an add-on to a notebook order. If you'd like to purchase one without the accompanying notebook please contact me and I can sort that out for you. Any orders without an accompanying notebook order will be cancelled.

The charms in the second picture slide onto the band.  Top row: flower, bronze-tone star, gold-tone star and silver-tone star.  The stars will also fit onto the spine, as pictured in the third photo, just let me know in the 'note to seller' if you'd prefer that.  Bottom row: gold-tone fox, silver-tone fox, standard owl, cute owl.

The fourth photo shows the options for the attached charms: straight onto the band or lobster clasp.  If you have a preference, please state it in the 'notes to seller'.  If I don't receive any instructions I'll go with what feels right to me at the time.

The fifth photo shows silver-tone infinity charm, bronze-tone infinity charm, and silver-tone Celtic knot.

The sixth photo shows neon purple, neon pink, and neon yellow infinity charms.

The seventh photo shows the coin charms.  Top row: silver-tone Never Never Give Up; silver-tone Believe in Love; silver-tone Dream.  Bottom row: bronze-tone Never Never Give Up; silver-tone Live Laugh Love; Well Behaved Women (this quote is actually about mid-wives, and is a reminder to remember those women who didn't rock the boat but were still important.  A double meaning).

On to the eighth photo. Top row: passport; white rabbit; sheep 1.  Middle Row: 2018; mermaid; silver-tone bird; sparkly star.  Bottom row: sheep 2; heart; silver-tone feather; pineapple.

Ninth photo.  Top row: bronze-tone bird; leaf; acorn - if you purchase both the leaf and acorn I can put them on the same jump-ring to form a charm like this: https://www.instagram.com/p/BbcVc1qnGes/?taken-by=inkbanditstn .  Just let me know in the 'notes to seller'.  Bottom row: tiny key; bronze-tone feather.

Tenth: blue babushka; red babushka; purple babushka; pink babushka


Bookmark charms can be found here: https://www.etsy.com/uk/listing/253416809/various-bookmark-charms-for-midori-or?ref=shop_home_active_12
